  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Energy Intake Compensation</measure>
    <time_frame>Average intake of energy during ad lib phase (9 days)</time_frame>
    <description>To assess energy intake compensation, we will assess average energy intake during the ad libitum food intake phase - which is the period after energy restriction- in young men and compare this to average energy intake in older men.
Average energy intake is assessed by measuring total megajoule of energy intake during nine days of the ad lib phase, and then divide it by nine (MJ/day)</description>
